trans-unit.source: Represents the <xref uid="langword_csharp_<CipherData>" name="<CipherData>" href=""></xref> element in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: 表示<xref uid="langword_csharp_<CipherData>" name="<CipherData>" href=""> </xref> XML 加密中的元素。

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 此类不能被继承。

trans-unit.source: The CipherData class represents the `<CipherData>` element in XML encryption.
trans-unit.target: CipherData 类表示`<CipherData>`XML 加密中的元素。

trans-unit.source: It is a required element that provides the encrypted data.
trans-unit.target: 它是提供加密的数据的必需的元素。

trans-unit.source: It must either contain the encrypted data as base64-encoded text of the `<CipherValue>` element, or provide a reference to an external location containing the encrypted data using the `<CipherReference>` element.
trans-unit.target: 它必须包含加密的数据的 base64 编码的文本作为`<CipherValue>`元素，或者提供对外部位置包含加密的数据使用的引用`<CipherReference>`元素。

trans-unit.source: In many cases, you do not need to directly create a new instance of the CipherData class.
trans-unit.target: 在许多情况下，你不需要直接创建 CipherData 类的新实例。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.EncryptedXml%2A>, <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>, and <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> classes create instances for you.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.EncryptedXml%2A>， <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData>，和<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey>类为你创建实例。</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedKey> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.EncryptedData> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.SignedXml.EncryptedXml%2A>

trans-unit.target: 1> [!NOTE]&1;> CipherData 对象可以具有<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherReference>属性或<xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherValue%2A>属性，但不是能同时。</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherData.CipherValue%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.Xml.CipherReference>
